7. e4{ Very blunt. White wants  d2 - d4  next without allowing  e5 - e4  in response. }
7. c5{ This should be Black's best try, locking the center and arguing that a lost tempo is not such a big deal in a closed position like this one. Fair enough, but... }
8. d3
8. Nc6
9. Ne1{ I definitely prefer White. He is much faster to get his f-pawn moving than Balck will be, and the plan of  Ne1 - c2  and  f2 - f4  plays itself. }
